ok can help you save your time and get working with Geronimo in matter of a few hours.',10,'resources/img/97818471944.jpg',412,' Packt Publishing',0,10,'Apache Geronimo 2.1',0,2009,2),(129,'2009-07-15 00:00:00','Jose Sandoval',7,2,'If you are already familiar with REST theory but are new to RESTful Java web services, and want to use the Java technology stack together with Java RESTful frameworks to create robust web services, this is the book for you.',6,'resources/img/97818471930.jpg',256,' Packt Publishing',0,6,'RESTful Java Web Services',0,2009,2),(130,'2009-04-15 00:00:00','David Thomas',8,6,'In today\'s world, JSF is one of the pivotal technologies for implementing middle- to large-scale web applications. With Trinidad, JSF developers have a powerful open source component framework at their fingertips.',9,'resources/img/97818471934.jpg',292,' Packt Publishing',4.5,5,'Apache MyFaces Trinidad 1.2',2,2009,5),(131,'2009-09-09 00:00:00','Anthony Chaves',7,4,'A data grid is a means of combining computing resources. Data grids provide a way to distribute object storage and add capacity on demand in the form of CPU, memory, and network resources from additional servers. All three resource types play an important role in how fast data can be processed, and how much data can be processed at once. WebSphere eXtreme Scale provides a solution to scalability issues through caching and grid technology. Working with a data grid requires new approaches to writing highly scalable software; this book covers both the practical eXtreme Scale libraries and design patterns that will help you build scalable software.',5,'resources/img/978184719118.jpg',292,' Packt Publishing',0,7,'IBM WebSphere eXtreme Scale 6',0,2009,4),(132,'2009-03-19 00:00:00','Demetrio Filocamo',6,4,'JBoss RichFaces is a rich component library for JavaServer Faces and an AJAX framework that allows easy integration of AJAX capabilities into complex business applications. Do you wish to eliminate the time involved 